{"tid":665853,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"melatonin一問","createTime":"2018-05-15T10:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T12:51:25.000Z","uid":86420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92f123a76d94beb8c9c98356148a1be5df29677b","tid":665853,"uid":86420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"最近都訓得好差，日日朝早晏晝好眼訓但到夜晚就好精神...<br />\n係床都碌至少一個鐘先訓得著，仲要訓個時發好多夢，<br />\n連續幾日2、3點訓但5點幾札醒到6點幾先起返身。<br />\n睇有巴絲講過melatonin比較天然，有無人試過gnc隻melatonin？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1392eaacada550f4ba8dd56caaaf0f314847d753","tid":665853,"uid":121260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"問醫生啦"},{"pid":"becd801efe88469b9765c44c9bfffdc57cdd57b2","tid":665853,"uid":86420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問醫生啦</blockquote><br />\n其實我諗應該係情緒影響，但唔想睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想俾屋企人知"},{"pid":"9ea439ccb21efad72e6f0e66fe44665de82b3949","tid":665853,"uid":77134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:35:52.000Z","msg":"唔好食 治標唔治本 反而會嚴重左 食慣左你身體唔識定時定侯製造melatonin"},{"pid":"69a21e25cf1ed4ab8216ae24b780e8bf4eb4c871","tid":665853,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"心病還需心藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9976e38eeb4f0383cb80a6320504245ae5abf2a6","tid":665853,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"真係唔好食 唔好依賴<br />\n非必要都唔好食藥<br />\n<br />\n可能你習慣左夜晚靜 易亂諗野？ 改變左個生理時鐘？<br />\n可以試下做多啲運動 整攰個人 等自己夜晚好訓啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163da1f5dcdc2f40a31255d340bbcff559840b16","tid":665853,"uid":86420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>心病還需心藥醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果佢搵返我 我一定會好返既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a33fce8f61c15ba236cbf2c7a795f898064c251","tid":665853,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:48:41.000Z","msg":"接受心理治療啦"},{"pid":"490f9fbf4b3ebe3701d557064cb4ced6962dcdf3","tid":665853,"uid":86420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係唔好食 唔好依賴<br />\n非必要都唔好食藥<br />\n<br />\n可能你習慣左夜晚靜 易亂諗野？ 改變左個生理時鐘？<br />\n可以試下做多啲運動 整攰個人 等自己夜晚好訓啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我就算返工返學過咗成日到夜晚都好精神...但我朝早同晏晝真係好攰，已經盡量唔俾自己晏晝訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011f28fd257378417fc6eacd60f66f39325401c9","tid":665853,"uid":86420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>接受心理治療啦</blockquote><br />\n我都想，但未嚴重到某個地步都唔想..."},{"pid":"fb7a3d0a623cf3e72e891b66b75f42d2413a468d","tid":665853,"uid":165879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:04:01.000Z","msg":"melatonin 係supplement 藥廠聲稱有效但係無solid evidence<br />\n(如果有佢就係正式西藥而唔係supplement)<br />\n主要係for jet lag<br />\n訓教問題可以先試promathezine<br />\n副作用比較少但係效力亦較低<br />\n如果要再勁啲有zopiclone同zolpidem Z-drug(俗稱白爪子)<br />\n會上瘾，而且會越食越純，所以唔可以長期食，好醫生suppose唔會開長期比你unless no other option<br />\n(下刪3768字)"},{"pid":"1f378b8c1909866e014215e8da2e2a763fed1a68","tid":665853,"uid":167465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"490f9fbf4b3ebe3701d557064cb4ced6962dcdf3","tid":665853,"uid":86420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係唔好食 唔好依賴<br />\n非必要都唔好食藥<br />\n<br />\n可能你習慣左夜晚靜 易亂諗野？ 改變左個生理時鐘？<br />\n可以試下做多啲運動 整攰個人 等自己夜晚好訓啲 <img sr